{"type": "article", "id": 41431, "title": "想放松你自己？请躺进“这盒薯条”里｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-30T23:19:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28095, "name": "HMM"}, {"id": 40970, "name": "Plants of Posters"}, {"id": 40971, "name": "BEST BEFORE 2065"}, {"id": 40972, "name": "DCW Editions"}, {"id": 40973, "name": "Brobygrafiska"}, {"id": 40974, "name": "Eric Standley"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 136, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170531071909Bhmp0TPsCKdRwM9i.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Plants of Posters by Federico Moreno &amp; Juan Frias</h3><p>为城市增添绿化也可以变成一个有趣且充满艺术感的过程，最近西班牙设计师 Federico Moreno 和 Juan Frias 创立了一个名为 Plants of Posters 的非营利企业，推广可以让海报自带花盆的模版。目前马德里的街头已经出现了一些采用这种模版制作的花盆海报，从照片上来看，它们并没有影响到海报实际的展示效果。如果你也想通过这种方式用花草装点墙面，可以通过它的<a href=\"http://www.plantsofposters.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>下载模版。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215612LD6lg9uzhMC4kPQi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215614XWkhQ15SG7TBNql6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215616OySD2nuY1FHo93ab.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215612BKrRIxpA6q03MS2U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.478667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>反正剪刀 by HMM</h3><p>收到包裹后发现手边没有安全刀，我们往往会用“劈腿”的剪刀或是其他工具应急。为了让人们不用再急中生智，致力于重新诠释日常工具的台湾品牌 <a href=\"https://www.hmm-shop.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HMM</a> 推出了这款正反都可以使用的“反正剪刀”。刀和用来开箱的握柄均由台湾工匠采用日本不锈钢打造而成，表面上有具备不粘性的特氟龙涂层，能利落地裁剪胶带，不拖泥带水。“反正剪刀”还配有一个磁性底座，可以大大方方地放在桌上。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/hmm\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 750 新台币起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215649jBrnLTW5sPa47IgK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648464\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215654n4Dp2fOcxgUW5itV.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648464\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215643uIlk3ArqoVtKBpdD.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648464\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215642Dm3CXp52kYUZvOej.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648464\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215654BD8xSfORh6ZqT0FH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.825000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Manet by BEST BEFORE 2065</h3><p>用“像是躺进了一盒炸薯条”来形容意大利设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.bb65.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BEST BEFORE 2065</a> 推出的模块化懒人沙发 Manet 再合适不过了。沙发由白色的“薯条盒”和 16 个可以自由移动的几何形沙发枕构成，你可以随心所欲地以自己喜欢的姿势在上面休息或是办公。枕头间的缝隙还能用作杂志架。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.maneteasychair.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">订购链接</a>，售价为 1570 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215733VRAc6tlhwOxSo8aL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705302157318dPax1ioHZp6G50A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705302157330hr7e4UuzdAqJLMv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705302157335IwGdLUSfKeyzP0j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215731glfXx7nB6TsCDbk8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ISP Lamp by DCW Editions</h3><p>还记得那个模仿法压壶、通过推拉调节明暗的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29724.html\">“液体灯”</a>吗？法国家居设计公司 <a href=\"http://dcw-editions.fr/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">DCW editions</a> 最近推出了一款有着异曲同工之妙的概念灯具 <a href=\"http://www.isp-lamps.com/index_EN.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">ISP</a>。打开金属灯罩末端，通过拉杆就可以沿着底座抽出一截管状的光芒，既优雅又富有趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215809p6oqriYNTlsPAtf5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.990625\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215754aSoOTJIny1QpB2VZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705302157530bLhUNjxQteK7qfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.215000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215752x70TBX439dybNSRH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.215294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Grenna Polkagriskokeri by Brobygrafiska</h3><p>瑞典小镇格兰纳（Gränna）是红白相间的拐杖形薄荷糖的故乡，设计团队 <a href=\"http://brobygrafiska.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brobygrafiska</a> 最近为当地糖果公司 <a href=\"http://polkagris.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Grenna Polkagriskokeri</a> 重新设计了一套包装。通透的淡粉色外壳配以简洁的白色文字看起来非常清爽，不会给人造成太过甜腻的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215907rfBcbL1q4KJZvjkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215908YKRyFrXSk0qwglPW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215907Uoy43Pgv9aGNnzbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215915ZVgXEzJ2ALdTtYG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530215916SxfLr21FRyIEq7uW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Paper Artworks by Eric Standley</h3><p>如果你喜欢哥特式或者伊斯兰建筑中错综复杂的花纹，不妨看看美国艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.eric-standley.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eric Standley</a> 利用激光切割而成的剪纸版复刻品。这些展现出分形几何之美的纸质装饰元素均由 140 多层纸张构成，需要数月的时间才能完成一幅。目前，辛辛那提的 <a href=\"http://www.martahewett.com/index.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marta Hewett Gallery</a> 正在举行 Standley 的个人展 <a href=\"http://www.martahewett.com/exhibits/exhibit-fancybox.php?cid=strata\" rel=\"nofollow\">Strata</a> ，展览将持续至 6 月 3 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705302200382gje4pGDBlN7h0Qy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.297000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530220038MkpTRBYxNiQLChoZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530220038IP7dXflB8SEkoWxM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.998000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530220038LyP7VXECrIf0nSh5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.330000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170530220039tQZimL4yARvzg359.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.561000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}